----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ’¡ Best Practices

* Break UI into small components
* Use props for data passing
* Use state for dynamic data
* Keep components simple
* Follow naming conventions

